#
# 2. Fill in your actual API keys above
#
# 3. Keep .env file secure - never commit to git
#
# 4. API Keys required for ws-server.js (full AI pipeline):
#    - ASSEMBLYAI_API_KEY (STT)
#    - GEMINI_API_KEY or GOOGLE_API_KEY (LLM)
